  • Method Details

    • addProduct

      boolean addProduct(String userId, String prodId, int demandQty)
      Adds a product to the user's demand list.
      Parameters:
      userId - The ID of the user.
      prodId - The ID of the product.
      demandQty - The quantity of the product demanded.
      Returns:
      true if the demand was successfully added, false otherwise.

    • addProduct

      boolean addProduct(DemandBean userDemandBean)
      Adds a product to the user's demand list using a DemandBean.
      Parameters:
      userDemandBean - The DemandBean object containing user and product demand details.
      Returns:
      true if the demand was successfully added, false otherwise.

    • removeProduct

      boolean removeProduct(String userId, String prodId)
      Removes a product from a user's demand list.
      Parameters:
      userId - The ID of the user.
      prodId - The ID of the product to remove from demand.
      Returns:
      true if the product was successfully removed from demand, false otherwise.

    • haveDemanded

      List<DemandBean> haveDemanded(String prodId)
      Retrieves a list of all users who have demanded a specific product.
      Parameters:
      prodId - The ID of the product.
      Returns:
      A list of DemandBean objects representing the demands for the product.
